{"version":3,"term":{"cols":80,"rows":24,"type":"xterm-kitty"},"timestamp":1782163860,"idle_time_limit":3.0,"command":"bash /tmp/recursion.sh","env":{"SHELL":"/bin/bash"}}
[0.005917, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m━━ Management-of-managements — a cluster that creates AND serves its own child (recursion) ━━\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;34mRoot creates host-mgmt (a management cluster). host-mgmt then runs its OWN Cluster API + CAAPH and\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000016, "o", "\u001b[1;34mcreates its OWN child (mgmt-child) — and hands it the SAME stack Root gives its regionals: ArgoCD +\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.00002, "o", "\u001b[1;34mregion-root + CNI. The child ends up decentralized, hosting its own tenant vCluster. No central SPOF.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000022, "o", "\u001b[1;34mThe whole chain was validated CLEAN-ROOM (torn down in reverse, rebuilt 100% from Git).\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[2.001828, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m━━ 1/4  Root creates host clusters via CAPI — one is role=management ━━\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[0.23484, "o", "  NAME        PHASE         ROLE\r\n  host-euw1   Provisioned   regional\r\n  host-mgmt   Provisioned   management\r\n"]
[3.007769, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m━━ 2/4  host-mgmt runs its OWN CAPI + CAAPH, and created a CHILD cluster (mgmt-child) ━━\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000022, "o", "\u001b[1;34mQuerying host-mgmt (via jump pod) — it has its own CAPI Cluster object 'mgmt-child':\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.309297, "o", "  NAMESPACE   NAME         CLUSTERCLASS   PHASE         AGE   VERSION\r\n  default     mgmt-child                  Provisioned   26h   \r\n"]
[0.00043, "o", "\u001b[1;34mhost-mgmt's ArgoCD delivers the child its CNI first (egg-and-chicken bootstrap):\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.38588, "o", "  NAME        SYNC STATUS   HEALTH STATUS\r\n  child-cni   Synced        Healthy\r\n"]
[3.002698, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m━━ 3/4  mgmt-child got its OWN ArgoCD + region-root — one rung down, decentralized ━━\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;34mQuerying mgmt-child (jump → into host-mgmt → into mgmt-child). Its own ArgoCD apps:\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.647141, "o", "  NAME                    SYNC STATUS   HEALTH STATUS\r\n  region-root             Synced        Healthy\r\n  vcluster-tenant-z-dev   Synced        Healthy\r\n  wl-tenant-z-dev         Synced        Healthy\r\n"]
[0.000895, "o", "\u001b[1;32m  -> mgmt-child runs its OWN ArgoCD that provisions ITS region's tenants. No central control plane.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[3.00385, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m━━ 4/4  The leaf — a tenant vCluster (tenant-z) running pg/api/web INSIDE mgmt-child ━━\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[1.804062, "o", "  NAME                                                              READY   STATUS    RESTARTS   AGE\r\n  tenant-z-customer-api-6848f9c899-j22t6-x-tenant-z-x--f4bae3a434   1/1     Running   0          24h\r\n  tenant-z-customer-web-69cd8b98f5-t6c7b-x-tenant-z-x--404979602d   1/1     Running   0          24h\r\n  tenant-z-postgres-0-x-tenant-z-x-vcluster-tenant-z-dev            1/1     Running   0          24h\r\n  vcluster-tenant-z-dev-0                                           1/1     Running   0          24h\r\n"]
[2.003308, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m━━ Root → host-mgmt (mgmt) → mgmt-child (own ArgoCD) → vcluster-tenant-z. Recursion, 100% GitOps. ━━\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
